a.title: Died peacefully but prematurely at age 51.

Gradual withdrawal and decent into depravity until finally perishing AD 37.
"... So much for Caligula as emperor; we must now tell of his career as a monster..." - Suetonius
Uncle of Caligula, found hiding behind the curtains and declared emperor. Incorporated Britain.
Murdered by wife and niece Agrippina to ensure the succession of her son Nero.
